Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.40,0:00:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A world... Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.00,0:00:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A world for you who seek freedom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.84,0:00:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,stretches out right before your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.01,0:00:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If your endless dreams are your guide,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.01,0:00:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,surpass them, under the flag of your beliefs!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.19,0:00:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Making a splash,\NI've just started on my search
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.69,0:00:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heading towards a world without end
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.20,0:00:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart bursting with enthusiasm,\NI'll go to the ends of the earth
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.37,0:00:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In search of light yet unseen
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.71,0:01:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the summer sun\Nsways the sails of my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.82,0:01:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the cue to open the door to a new world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.33,0:01:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sailing through the rocky waves of despair
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.34,0:01:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We head beyond the horizon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.01,0:01:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Making a splash,\NI've just started on my search
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.68,0:01:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heading towards a world without end
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.19,0:01:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart bursting with enthusiasm,\NI'll go to the ends of the earth
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.36,0:01:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In search of light yet unseen
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.67,0:01:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am... I am... the man\Nwho'll be King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.88,0:02:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please... stop fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.93,0:02:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The battle will end...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.44,0:02:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rain falling right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.64,0:02:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...will fall again as it used to...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.01,0:02:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...since our nightmares are... all over...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.30,0:02:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Farewell to Arms!\NPirates and Different Ideas of Justice"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.18,0:03:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The nightmares are over...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.48,0:03:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.15,0:03:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way what happened\Nwas just "nightmares"!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.68,0:03:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! We saw the king\Nattack Nanohana with our own eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.45,0:03:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! Koza-san was\Nalso shot by the Royal Army!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.02,0:03:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you explain the Royal\NArmy's misconduct up until now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.26,0:03:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not good enough for\Nthose who fell in this rebellion!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.70,0:03:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.71,0:03:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drop your weapons! Royal Army!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.72,0:03:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chaka-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.72,0:03:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.99,0:03:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.93,0:03:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.53,0:04:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ma-ma-ma...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.23,0:04:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too, Rebel Army!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.44,0:04:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... Igaram-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.44,0:04:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Squad Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.51,0:04:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Igaram...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.52,0:04:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Igaram-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.86,0:04:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us meet safely at our motherland.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.90,0:04:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the old pervert from Whisky Peak!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.00,0:04:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--So he was alive!\N--Uhm, who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.11,0:04:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, can you talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.18,0:04:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.18,0:04:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the boy from Nanohana...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.15,0:04:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right... He's the kid who\Nwas harmed by the Royal Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.22,0:04:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not true... They weren't\Nthe ones who hurt me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.69,0:05:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, listen! I saw it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.46,0:05:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just can't feel relaxed without this on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.50,0:05:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's vague!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.57,0:05:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right... This battle was\Na plot from the beginning...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.88,0:05:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Koza-san!\N--Leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.25,0:05:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will explain everything...\Nthat happened to this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.53,0:05:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, drop your weapons!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.31,0:05:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vivi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.11,0:05:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's... everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.49,0:06:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, walk steady.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.99,0:06:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh... Well, listen... I'm coming down\Nwith "if I walk more, I'll die" disease...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.59,0:06:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then stay there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.76,0:06:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Well, w-wait! Whoa! Hey! Hey! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.60,0:06:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why're you pulling me by my foot?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.10,0:06:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hm?\N--Found him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.44,0:06:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.91,0:06:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh... Thanks for carrying\Nthat guy on your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.85,0:06:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's one of ours. I'll take him now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.55,0:06:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you're the pirates who\Nbrought Vivi back to this country?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.02,0:06:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you, old guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.26,0:06:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.09,0:06:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.16,0:06:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, it's Vivi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.60,0:06:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.03,0:06:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vivi-chan's father?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.63,0:06:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you the King?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.54,0:06:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I prepared myself to die at\None point, but he saved me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.04,0:06:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When his body was exhausted\Nafter the fight with Crocodile,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.28,0:07:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he carried two people\Nand rushed above ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.78,0:07:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What unbelievable strength...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.08,0:07:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then there's no more need\Nto worry about the poison?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.09,0:07:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. It should be neutralized by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.66,0:07:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But his injuries need to\Nbe treated... Yours, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.43,0:07:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, Vivi, go already.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.50,0:07:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What?\N--Go back to the Square.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.00,0:07:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! The rebellion has finally stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.01,0:07:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wouldn't be proper if the king\Nor princess didn't say a few words.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.51,0:07:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... then I'll tell them about you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.25,0:07:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vivi-chan. You know how it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.29,0:07:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're notorious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.99,0:07:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have no intention of\Ngetting involved with a country.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.02,0:07:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.23,0:07:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going on ahead to\Nthe palace. I'm exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.88,0:08:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, understood, Captain Smoker.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.95,0:08:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then Crocodile-san was...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.09,0:08:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy was the ringleader for everything...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.43,0:08:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good heavens... I can't believe it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.33,0:08:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look at that! It's the Navy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.57,0:08:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were told that a Baroque Works-owned\Nartificial rain-making ship
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.71,0:08:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was discovered with dance powder on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.01,0:08:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Crocodile, president of the\Nsecret crime syndicate Baroque Works
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.15,0:08:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and one of the Seven Warlords of the Sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.46,0:08:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did the gator go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.60,0:09:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the name of Navy Headquarters, an agency\Ndirectly under the World Government,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.17,0:09:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hereby strip you of your\Nauthorization to capture enemy ships,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.57,0:09:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as well as all the titles and rights\Nbestowed upon you by the Government.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.30,0:09:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait and see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.95,0:09:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've done an irreparable thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.42,0:09:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leader...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.83,0:10:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what to say to them...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.73,0:10:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just natural to regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.87,0:10:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That unbearable feeling is also natural...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.37,0:10:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,King...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.60,0:10:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Majesty...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.37,0:10:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We lost so much and gained nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.95,0:10:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, this is a step forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.88,0:10:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter who you fought against,\Nthe battle did occur and has now ended...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.53,0:10:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,King...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.96,0:10:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one can make the past go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.00,0:10:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Overcome this war and survive...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.42,0:11:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He truly is without equal...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.72,0:11:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alabasta Kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.00,0:11:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The battle that will be\Nengraved in history and...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.88,0:11:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the battle that will never be told...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.89,0:11:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...have ended...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.37,0:11:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smoker-kun! What on earth is this rain?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.91,0:12:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you used the Dance Powder?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.61,0:12:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.88,0:12:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do know better than to commit a crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.29,0:12:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Alabasta King kept\Nhis hands off of this powder.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.99,0:12:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the point in me going\Nagainst his morals now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.23,0:12:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, excuse me. I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.07,0:12:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe the "White Hunter"\Nof all men would say something sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.40,0:12:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if you've mellowed out a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.51,0:12:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's none of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.51,0:12:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, you're really something,\Nusing my elite unit just to look for a ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.25,0:12:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very upset... I'm upset!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.89,0:12:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We joined the Navy in the\Nsame year. Don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.02,0:12:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You always say that. I pity Tashigi\Nfor the troubles you put her through.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.56,0:12:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, take in\Nthis artificial rain-making ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.43,0:12:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.90,0:13:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And also, Tashigi will bring\NCrocodile here. So take him, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.31,0:13:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a break! What makes\Nyou think you can be so selfish?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.32,0:13:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heads!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.19,0:13:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's tails. You lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.63,0:13:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really selfish, you know that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.93,0:13:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't changed a bit since we\Njoined the Navy. I'm disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.77,0:13:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine. I'm well aware of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.91,0:13:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's an order.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.58,0:13:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sergeant Major! This is\Na very rare opportunity!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.05,0:13:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once they come to, we won't be able to...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.52,0:13:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will not allow you to lay\Na hand on them right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.79,0:13:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why?! They're all sitting ducks right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.26,0:14:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-On top of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.60,0:14:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leader... Are your injuries okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.64,0:14:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not gonna die, are you?\NUhm, Toto-ojisan was... Yuba was...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.98,0:14:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vivi... Looks like you're still\Nthe worrywart as always...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.15,0:14:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know about Yuba,\Nbut my stubborn old man won't die,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.65,0:14:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,no matter what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.19,0:14:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Leader...\N--And I've got his blood in my veins.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.96,0:14:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As soon as I get treated, I'll head to Yuba.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.00,0:14:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep you updated... so don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.34,0:14:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.74,0:14:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's raining!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.61,0:14:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rain! It's raining for\Nthe first time in three years!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.58,0:14:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This rain will end the rebellion!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.61,0:14:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our foolish sons will come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.72,0:14:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's raining!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.90,0:15:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just how long are you gonna\Nstay so stubborn, old man?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.24,0:15:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuba is already finished.\NWhat're you gonna do here by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.21,0:15:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you gonna die with the city? Old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.05,0:15:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look... Koza. The rain has fallen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.45,0:15:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just three years... That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.50,0:15:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right... rain...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.11,0:15:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rain is no longer forced and\Nfalls endlessly within the kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.54,0:16:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vivi-sama... You're still up?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.54,0:16:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Igaram...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.64,0:16:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.48,0:16:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.95,0:16:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.92,0:16:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanna keep watching this rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.37,0:16:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About Pell...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.97,0:17:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is the most dignified and\Nstrongest among the warriors I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.18,0:17:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.98,0:17:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to say "thank you" to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.49,0:17:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'd be... greatly honored by that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.93,0:17:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Smoker, Miss Hina!\NSergeant Major Tashigi has arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.74,0:17:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.21,0:17:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while, Tashigi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.45,0:17:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.25,0:17:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello... I'm... a little tired,\Nso I'll go get some rest...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.96,0:17:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Smoker, I've just returned!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.93,0:17:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, thanks for your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.20,0:17:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard about what happened\Nwith the Straw Hats.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.97,0:17:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.17,0:18:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I helped the pirates and let our\Nopportunity to capture them slip away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.21,0:18:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that my actions\Nwere shameful as a marine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.78,0:18:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you apologize?\NDidn't you follow your justice?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.49,0:18:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... that's not it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.69,0:18:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sergeant Major...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.86,0:18:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just... didn't have any other choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.80,0:18:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Losers can't speak about justice.\NWe're in that kind of sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.48,0:18:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did the gator go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.18,0:18:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.05,0:18:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when I knew where the enemy was,\Nall I could do was tell him where...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.99,0:18:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when I knew the time of the attack,\Nall I could do was assist them...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.99,0:19:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was... no justice that I could follow...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.84,0:19:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who you thought you\Nwere on par with up until recently
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.51,0:19:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are becoming more\Nnotorious and rising rapidly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.41,0:19:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They know that in this sea,\Nthey'll die if they don't rise up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.05,0:19:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go forward or die?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.59,0:19:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who decided to come to this sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.76,0:19:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me... but I'll go rest a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.55,0:19:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.35,0:19:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're frustrated enough\Nto cry, become stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.40,0:20:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.44,0:20:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish you guys had guts like that, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.48,0:20:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, bring them to the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.95,0:20:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.02,0:20:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Smoker! You have a\Ncommunication from Headquarters!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.45,0:20:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.52,0:20:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Navy Headquarters.\NIs this Captain Smoker?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.49,0:20:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.76,0:20:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In regards to your subduing Crocodile,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.73,0:20:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's been decided that the top\Nofficials of the Government
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.63,0:20:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are going to give you and\NSergeant Major Tashigi a medal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.57,0:20:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Subduing...? Hey, wait a sec!\NIt wasn't us who took Crocodile down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.97,0:20:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were they really listening to the report?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.14,0:20:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, each of you will\Nbe promoted by one rank, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.22,0:21:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Listen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.32,0:21:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ones who've been fighting Crocodile\Nand his Baroque Works all this time
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.59,0:21:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,were the Straw Hat gang.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.86,0:21:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use, Smoker-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.83,0:21:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Government is probably\Ngoing to cover up this incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.56,0:21:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone at the Government was\Noutwitted with regard to Alabasta's crisis.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.50,0:21:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think they can tell the world\Nthat it was saved by pirates?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.97,0:21:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, we'd like both of you to\Nattend the medal award ceremony and...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.44,0:21:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.34,0:21:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smoker-kun! Accept it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.88,0:21:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you disobey the top officials,\Nyou don't know what'll happen to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.48,0:21:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We took Crocodile down?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.85,0:21:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My subordinate is in tears\Nbecause we couldn't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.29,0:21:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you... Could you tell the old\Ngeezers at the top something for me...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.50,0:21:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Huh?\N--Smoker-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.70,0:21:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Go to hell"!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.75,0:22:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which direction should I run towards\Nto see a more wonderful tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.89,0:22:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I took the helm and opened the\Nmiraculous map that I stored in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.66,0:22:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I aimed for the sky and sought out\Nmy dreams, though at times I got lost
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.87,0:22:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't a dream; when I met you,\NI discovered the wonderful person in me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.31,0:22:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With just a bit of courage,\NI gained something grand
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.51,0:22:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's the time for my "wish"\Nto become my "pledge"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.85,0:22:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shining ray! Find your brand new way
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.79,0:22:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's sketch out the tale of the future
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.89,0:22:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll put all my feelings\Nin a brand new wind now
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.80,0:22:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shining ray! Find your brand new way
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.77,0:22:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A never-ending journey to be together
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.94,0:23:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll chase after you\Nwherever you go, Shining ray
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.41,0:23:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uhm, I'm Usopp, chief of\Nthe party department.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.22,0:23:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to all of you, we were able to\Ntake down the detestable Crocodile...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.29,0:23:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? Hey! Don't eat it yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.02,0:23:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, when we think of it,\Nit was a tough battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.39,0:23:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay! Well then, everyone!\NEat, drink and party like crazy for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.80,0:23:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.20,0:23:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.66,0:23:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Pirates' Banquet and\NOperation Escape from Alabasta!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.93,0:23:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.27,0:23:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
